{"tid":913518,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港珠澳大橋金巴將強制使用「微信公眾號」購買車票","createTime":"2018-11-23T12:52:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-29T09:52:16.000Z","uid":79563,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4244cce0bf19f2a16c1ab7a080c91f626b7b54d5","tid":913518,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T12:52:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1429837_1_L_20181123202530.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1429837_1_L_20181123202530.jpg&h=09626cbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n俗稱「金巴」的港珠澳大橋穿梭巴士，明日起要求所有由珠海口岸前往香港口岸的旅客，必須提前透過「微信公眾號」購買車票，並實施限量售票。本台致電「金巴」的香港服務熱線查詢，職員回覆說，香港居民如果沒有內地的支付工具，可以透過朋友提前購票，亦可以持香港居民身份證或回鄉證，親身到珠海口岸的售票櫃位尋求協助，理論上可在現場處理購票事宜，但不能保證一定能夠成功購票。<br />\n<br />\n被問到出售給香港居民和內地居民的車票數量限制，是否分開計算，職員就未有正面回應，只重申可以向櫃位職員查詢，並表示這兩天的票量比較緊張，根據測試系統的數據，明天由珠海前往香港的車票已經全部售罄。<br />\n<br />\n港珠澳大橋穿梭巴士實施微信購買後，珠海口岸的售票區域只提供二維碼取票服務，但微信公眾號只能使用內地的微信支付或內地銀行卡，不能使用香港版的微信支付或信用卡。"},{"pid":"35ab7b5cfb5f202ca96bda643296bcba569bf4ac","tid":913518,"uid":137725,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T12:53:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">關我撚事</span></strong></span><br />\n有時間笑多陣浸中爆炸單野仲好啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 單野on9咁多"},{"pid":"3344ffbb8463b14da9819b379d04ee68fa39ead5","tid":913518,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T12:56:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98e4a14e96cb60f752d62811eae34f6aadb585be","tid":913518,"uid":63154,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T12:59:35.000Z","msg":"香港版都唔得，笑死，班用家仲要係老野多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31f6b68068451053020e678a125b2a05334a3f82","tid":913518,"uid":35814,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T13:03:08.000Z","msg":"即係<br />\n1：想確定買飛數而決定請幾多part time開車，但有信心唔係應該長開多班次咩？<br />\n<br />\n2：就算有港人因工作需要經珠海番轉頭，但唔好意思，一般港人都要做二等人，除非肯賣個人資料，皇崗巴就算冇八達通都可以比現金啦，低能嘅！<br />\n<br />\n3：方便唔正規嘅團一次過買多張飛<br />\n<br />\n我真係祝人仔快啲大跌快啲支爆，到時冇人想落黎呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4130ea5c5fb595fdb20fb0c472b35d6eb6c703a","tid":913518,"uid":188178,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T13:06:20.000Z","msg":"錢就香港俾最多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72bbf88a110d03dd1f6555349aad072b0cf6ed32","tid":913518,"uid":25183,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T13:11:52.000Z","msg":"香港出發有去冇回<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9902c3bc9260761e1f65b692d3e1836b34ca72f3","tid":913518,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T13:14:44.000Z","msg":"又搞港獨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6922648a4f6f15a92b89a12d2b094928e6977dec","tid":913518,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T13:15:46.000Z","msg":"身有屎先驚論"},{"pid":"15e5ace21e3b88b6bd1985fb22a6a4137258f143","tid":913518,"uid":149978,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"35ab7b5cfb5f202ca96bda643296bcba569bf4ac","tid":913518,"uid":137725,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T12:53:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">關我撚事</span></strong></span><br />\n有時間笑多陣浸中爆炸單野仲好啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 單野on9咁多"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T07:30:42.000Z","msg":"On9<br />\n呢單野香港人好大獲 <br />\n大陸仔開大陸版微信支付